  "text": "To further characterize MSC from MDS, differentiation assays recommended by The International Society for Cellular Therapy were performed. [CITATION_1] Adipocytic and osteoblastic differentiation assays were performed in five cases, (8, 10, 14, 16 and 31) . Chondrocytic differentiation was performed in three cases (8, 10 and 14) .",
